          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="card__title"><span class="card__title-icon" aria-hidden="true">•</span>Direct period</h3>
            <p class="card__text">The period and the semicolon are swapped, in favor of the most used character.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="card__title"><span class="card__title-icon" aria-hidden="true">@</span>Accessible at sign and hashtag</h3>
            <p class="card__text">On the top-left key: @ for emails, # with Shift.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="card__title"><span class="card__title-icon" aria-hidden="true">{ }</span>Accessible developer symbols</h3>
            <p class="card__text">Access to { } \ | [ ] with AltGr on D F G H J K, from the home row.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="card__title"><span class="card__title-icon" aria-hidden="true">Á</span>Accents on the ù key</h3>
